{"tid":1154241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普:將向農民提供150億美元援助","createTime":"2019-05-14T06:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T23:25:47.000Z","uid":28765,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d1f3b0a95bcd0399fd8f85cdf77c850a11e0ba17","tid":1154241,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:56:07.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普表示，受到中國提高關稅打擊的美國農民，將可望獲得150億美元援助。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮回應記者提問時指出，將協助農民擺脫受出口減少的影響，涉及投放金額為150億美元，來源包括從加徵中國貨關稅獲得的收益。但他沒有提及細節。<br />\n<br />\n美國農業部長珀杜(Sonny Perdue)上周五表示，特朗普已經要求他制訂計劃，協助農民紓困。<br />\n<br />\n如果真的落實援助農民，將是華府第二次因應關稅問題對農民提供援助。去年，美國政府已為農民提供120億美元援助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2136175/特朗普%3A將向農民提供150億美元援助\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2136175%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%253A%E5%B0%87%E5%90%91%E8%BE%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B150%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%8F%B4%E5%8A%A9&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=3a3430d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2136175/特朗普%3A將向農民提供150億美元援助</a>"},{"pid":"773c8b19b98417458639189cf0dfaaff39e3d0dc","tid":1154241,"uid":78666,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:56:39.000Z","msg":"撚狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77b3509c84db403cfea9e2c9a2e4df136e56103","tid":1154241,"uid":155095,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:58:05.000Z","msg":"美國農民正廢柴，要政府補貼<br />\n<br />\n中國農民連補助都唔使，又贏"},{"pid":"00447a69f4998f79227bdc29c9c418acafdec411","tid":1154241,"uid":25468,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"c77b3509c84db403cfea9e2c9a2e4df136e56103","tid":1154241,"uid":155095,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:58:05.000Z","msg":"美國農民正廢柴，要政府補貼<br />\n<br />\n中國農民連補助都唔使，又贏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:12:49.000Z","msg":"支那農業點會無補貼呀 , 4年補貼左